trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para o evento de <see cref="E:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved" /> .
Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: A tracking service that implements the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification> interface raises a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> event to notify the runtime tracking infrastructure that new instances of a particular workflow <xref:System.Type> should no longer be tracked.
trans-unit.target: Um serviço de acompanhamento que implementa o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification> interface gera um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> eventos para notificar o infra-estrutura de controle de tempo de execução que novas instâncias de um determinado fluxo de trabalho <xref:System.Type> não devem ser controladas.

trans-unit.source: The tracking service uses a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs> to provide the workflow <xref:System.Type> to the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: O serviço de acompanhamento usa um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs> para fornecer o fluxo de trabalho <xref:System.Type> a infra-estrutura de controle de tempo de execução.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> uses a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs> when it raises the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService.ProfileRemoved?displayProperty=nameWithType> event.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> usa um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs> quando ele gera o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService.ProfileRemoved?displayProperty=nameWithType> evento.

trans-unit.source: After a tracking service raises the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> event, the runtime tracking infrastructure will no longer associate a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> with the specified workflow <xref:System.Type> for that tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Depois de um serviço de controle gera o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> evento, a infra-estrutura de controle de tempo de execução não vai associar um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> com o fluxo de trabalho especificado <xref:System.Type> para esse serviço de controle.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs" />.

trans-unit.source: If you use this constructor when you raise a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> event inside a tracking service, you must explicitly set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Se você usar este construtor quando você gerar um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> evento dentro de um serviço de controle, você deve definir explicitamente <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The workflow <see cref="T:System.Type" /> for which the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile" /> should be removed.
trans-unit.target: O fluxo de trabalho <see cref="T:System.Type" /> para o qual o <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile" /> deve ser removido.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs" /> class that applies to the specified workflow <see cref="T:System.Type" />.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs" /> que se aplica ao fluxo de trabalho <see cref="T:System.Type" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: A new instance of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs> is created with <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> set to the specified <xref:System.Type>.
trans-unit.target: Uma nova instância da <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs> é criada com <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> definido como especificado <xref:System.Type>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the workflow <see cref="T:System.Type" /> for which the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile" /> should be removed.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o fluxo de trabalho <see cref="T:System.Type" /> para o qual o <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile" /> deve ser removido.
O <see cref="T:System.Type" /> de um fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> specifies the workflow <xref:System.Type> for which a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> no longer exists, and which, therefore, should no longer be tracked by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> Especifica o fluxo de trabalho <xref:System.Type> para os quais um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> não existir, e que, portanto, devem não ser controladas pelo tempo de execução de infra-estrutura de rastreamento.
